*Željela* je da doživi pravu ljubav. (She wanted to experience true love.)

Ona je *željela* da bude srećna. (She wanted to be happy.)

*Željele* su da putuju širom sveta. (They wanted to travel around the world.)

Oni su *željeli* da imaju svoju decu. (They wanted to have their own children.)

*Željeli* smo da budemo srećni. (We wanted to be happy.)

Ona je *želela* da ode na more. (She wanted to go to the sea.)